Important Protocols & Frameworks (focus on the protocols from an infosec perspective) 
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Note: I have excluded protocols that are still in use but are no longer recommended for security or efficiency reasons. Those protocols will be mentioned in a separate document.

